Date:   Fri Mar 13 21:16:12 2026 +0800

    feat: add role-based session access control

    Implement role-based access control so non-admin org members can only view their own session transcripts, enforced both server-side (API) and client-side (UI). Adds userRole and isOrgAdmin to request context, prevents unauthorized session detail access, hides view links in timeline, and blocks navigation in session lists. Improves DataTable component with per-row clickability for explicit UX.

    Co-Authored-By: Claude Haiku 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>
    Entire-Checkpoint: 5542bbee2ba1

